                    <span>I really recommend this book, because it's easy to find your own decorating style in it. The book includes a very helpfull test in which you can discover the best decoration style for you , based on your personality (formal, sleek, etc).
<br />The photographs are very good and it contains information about colour, fabrics, ilumination and other very important issues to consider when you want to decorate a room.
<br />It has modern decorating ideas combined with good taste and common sense. Very good!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Tells you what the pros know</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>9</span>
